Created: 2026-05-27T00:00:00Z
CreatorComment: <text>
SPDX SBOM for the handheld-multi-modal application
(federal-aerospace/apps/handheld-multi-modal).

Scope: third-party open-source components consumed by the application —
container base images, Python pip dependencies of the locally built
whisper-stt service, OS packages installed in those images, and the
external VIPPET tool the deployment integrates with.

Intel-authored sources in this repository are NOT enumerated as packages;
only third-party dependencies are listed, per the SBOM request.
</text>

