PackageCopyrightText: <text>Copyright (C) 2026 Intel Corporation</text>
PackageSummary: <text>Full-stack edge AI inference and observability platform combining an OpenVINO-based LLM server, a Whisper speech-to-text service, a chat UI, and a Grafana metrics stack, packaged as a Docker Compose deployment.</text>

